35
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:50,540
Activity diagram, business process diagram,

36
00:01:50,540 --> 00:01:55,085
business use cases, dataflow diagram, data dictionary,

37
00:01:55,085 --> 00:01:58,890
entity-relationship diagram, role map, state diagram,

38
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:00,600
and SWAT analyses.

39
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:04,080
There are many other tools like this in the same genre,

40
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:10,000
